name: The Merry Orchestra
description:
The Merry Orchestra travels from place to place, engrossed in a never-ending parade.
Many are drawn by the whimsical tunes and enchanting aura of festive joy, overcome by a strong desire for revelry and wild celebration.
And for each dreamer that joins their parade, foolishly believing it to be a temporary entertainment, the Merry Orchestra grows larger and wilder.
